          <h3>Required Certifications</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:12px;">✅ High School Diploma / GED<br>✅ BOSIET (offshore only)<br>✅ Basic first aid / CPR (often provided)<br>⬜ IWCF Well Control (not required at entry)</p>
          <a href="/careers/certifications" class="card-link">Full Certification Guide →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top:1px;border:1px solid var(--iron);border-radius:0 0 4px 4px;">
          <h3>Related Reading</h3>
          <a href="/careers/salary" class="card-link">→ Full Salary Guide</a><br><br>
          <a href="/careers/driller" class="card-link">→ How to Become a Driller</a><br><br>
          <a href="/safety" class="card-link">→ Rig Safety Overview</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
